    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know how much longer i can keep doing this. it's just so exhausting trying to pretend i'm normal or that i even want to be part of this world. it feels like i'm just performing a role every single day and it's never gonna change. like, what's even the point of trying to fit into a world that wasn't built for me?",
